{"arkId":"cl010104371","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104371","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre en forme de coquille","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre en forme de coquille"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1650","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 4","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1650,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Sermand","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7035","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre en forme de coquille ; bo\u00eetier piriforme \u00e0 deux couvercles nervur\u00e9s mont\u00e9s \u00e0 charni\u00e8res. Armature du couvercle du cadran grav\u00e9e de feuillages et stri\u00e9e ; armature du couvercle oppos\u00e9 grav\u00e9e de mani\u00e8re similaire. Carrure orn\u00e9e d\u0027une frise de feuilles de vigne et de grappes de raisin. Bouton moulur\u00e9 ; pendant disparu. Plaque du cadran grav\u00e9e d\u0027une vue de village et de rinceaux o\u00f9 apparaissent une t\u00eate d\u0027angelot et deux lapins ; elle supporte un anneau \u00e0 chiffres romains. Mouvement muni d\u0027un coq et cliquet ajour\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux fleuris. Echappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Piliers en forme de balustre.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Sermand [signature ponctu\u00e9e d\u0027une fleurette]","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3","displayDimension":"3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2","displayDimension":"2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Gen\u00e8ve (Europe-\u003ESuisse) (ou Paris) ; Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France) (ou Gen\u00e8ve)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"},{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"},{"value":"Gen\u00e8ve"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliographyDetail":"n